SOLUTION(EV3(<<'END_SOLUTION'));
$PAR
SOLUTION:
$PAR
The probability that she does $BITAL not $EITAL leave her iClicker in the first four classes and then does leave it in the fifth is \( \left(\frac{3}{4}\right)^4 \left(\frac{1}{4}\right)\).
